@startuml
!pragma layout smetana
title 05. Sub-Agent LangGraph Orchestration (Workflow)

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor<<Node>> #E8F8F5
  BorderColor<<Node>> #16A085
}

state "load_context" as LoadContext <<Node>> : 로컬 히스토리 및 문맥 복원
state "select_tools" as SelectTools <<Node>> : 실행 가능한 도구 계획 수립 (Planner)
state "execute_tools" as ExecuteTools <<Node>> : 계획된 도구 순차 실행 (Executor)
state "finalize_context" as FinalizeContext <<Node>> : 실행 결과 요약 및 히스토리 업데이트
state "compose_response" as ComposeResponse <<Node>> : 최종 사용자 응답 합성 (Composer)

[*] --> LoadContext
LoadContext --> SelectTools

SelectTools --> ExecuteTools : [plans exists]
SelectTools --> ComposeResponse : [no more plans or max iterations]

ExecuteTools --> FinalizeContext
FinalizeContext --> SelectTools : [loop back for multi-turn planning]

ComposeResponse --> [*]

note right of SelectTools
  - LlmPlanningService 사용
  - McpToolRegistry에서 툴 스키마 로드
end note

note right of ExecuteTools
  - McpToolExecutor 사용
  - MCP 서버와 JSON-RPC 통신
end note

note right of ComposeResponse
  - LlmResponseComposeService 사용
  - 스트리밍 응답(Chunk) 발행
end note
@enduml
